query:
SELECT ce.id, ce.courseId, ce.enrollmentDate, ce.traineeCount, ce.paidAmount, c.name as courseName, c.startDate as courseStartDate
FROM courseEnrollments ce 
JOIN courses c ON ce.courseId = c.id
WHERE c.name LIKE '%تسويق%' OR c.name LIKE '%التسويق%'
ORDER BY c.startDate DESC;
